## What to do
The `_periodDates(String scheduleId)` method (line 82) finds the anchor schedule and walks backward/forward by `anchor.userId` to determine the period date range. After a prórroga swap, the anchor's `userId` has changed from `requesterId` to `nextUserId`, so the method walks using the wrong user and may show incorrect dates.

