### 1. cancelExtensionRequest(String requestId)
Deletes a pending extension request. This allows the requester to cancel before the next user accepts/rejects.

```dart
/// Cancels (deletes) a pending extension request.
///
/// Throws if the request is not in 'pending' status.
Future<void> cancelExtensionRequest(String requestId) async {
